    • setDateProvider

      public DatedList<T> setDateProvider(Supplier<Dater<T>> provider)

      Sets the date provider - Dater supplier.

      Dater is a function that takes a T object and a LocalDate, and returns JComponent to represent the given day for the given object.

      Date provider can have fields with EditorEntry to let the user configure it

      Parameters:
      provider - - provider to use
